CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 26, 1956, pg. 17 reads: "A Pair Of Dolls - Carol and Shona McKethen, grandchildren of Mrs. Fannie Prince, a beauty shop owner, modeled these hand-crocheted dresses and hats in recent beauticians' style show. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Carol McKethen wearing crocheted dress and hat, standing on stairs in Fort Pitt Hotel for Beautician's fashion and hair style show
